00:53:22.730 --> 00:53:25.280 align:middle line:84%
was really about
becoming conscious.

00:53:25.280 --> 00:53:27.800 align:middle line:84%
And there's an aspect of
the Vedas called Dhanurveda.

00:53:27.800 --> 00:53:30.110 align:middle line:84%
Dhaner, the Dhanurasana
of the Bow Asana.

00:53:30.110 --> 00:53:32.210 align:middle line:84%
It has to do with
pulling back the bow.

00:53:32.210 --> 00:53:37.880 align:middle line:84%
And the golden four
words in Vedic science

00:53:37.880 --> 00:53:41.450 align:middle line:84%
are establish being
and perform action,

00:53:41.450 --> 00:53:44.120 align:middle line:84%
or what's called
Yogastha Kuru Karmani.

00:53:44.120 --> 00:53:45.530 align:middle line:90%
You pull back the bow.

00:53:45.530 --> 00:53:47.450 align:middle line:90%
You establish being.

00:53:47.450 --> 00:53:48.710 align:middle line:90%
You take aim.

00:53:48.710 --> 00:53:50.390 align:middle line:90%
You hold it really still.

00:53:50.390 --> 00:53:52.460 align:middle line:84%
And you take action
from that deep place

00:53:52.460 --> 00:53:54.260 align:middle line:90%
of inner peace and calm.

00:53:54.260 --> 00:53:56.450 align:middle line:84%
If I'm holding the arrow
and I'm moving it around,

00:53:56.450 --> 00:53:57.710 align:middle line:84%
I have no idea what
I'm going to hit.

00:53:57.710 --> 00:53:58.590 align:middle line:90%
It's going to be dangerous.

00:53:58.590 --> 00:53:59.210 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: It could go anywhere.

00:53:59.210 --> 00:53:59.500 align:middle line:90%
>>DOUILLARD: Right.

00:53:59.500 --> 00:54:01.070 align:middle line:84%
And it's exponentially
distorted,

00:54:01.070 --> 00:54:02.730 align:middle line:90%
if I'm moving this thing around.

00:54:02.730 --> 00:54:06.470 align:middle line:84%
But if I establish being
and then take action

00:54:06.470 --> 00:54:09.030 align:middle line:84%
and take action from
that place of silence,

00:54:09.030 --> 00:54:10.160 align:middle line:90%
it's transformational.

00:54:10.160 --> 00:54:12.700 align:middle line:84%
It's a karmic
transformational action.

00:54:12.700 --> 00:54:18.130 align:middle line:84%
So the point of Vedic science
is for us to still our body.

00:54:18.130 --> 00:54:19.340 align:middle line:90%
Establish being.

00:54:19.340 --> 00:54:22.370 align:middle line:84%
Yoga, breathing,
meditation, living in sync

00:54:22.370 --> 00:54:24.305 align:middle line:84%
with the natural
cycles, going downstream

00:54:24.305 --> 00:54:25.430 align:middle line:90%
with the current of nature.

00:54:25.430 --> 00:54:26.240 align:middle line:90%
Being still.

00:54:26.240 --> 00:54:27.110 align:middle line:90%
Being in nature.

00:54:27.110 --> 00:54:30.140 align:middle line:84%
Restore the silence, the
awareness, and appreciation

00:54:30.140 --> 00:54:31.620 align:middle line:90%
of inner space.

00:54:31.620 --> 00:54:34.590 align:middle line:84%
And then from that clarity,
bring the body back

00:54:34.590 --> 00:54:35.390 align:middle line:90%
into balance.

00:54:35.390 --> 00:54:36.190 align:middle line:90%
Vata, Pitta, Kapha.

00:54:36.190 --> 00:54:38.150 align:middle line:84%
Bring the body digestion
back into balance.

00:54:38.150 --> 00:54:41.420 align:middle line:84%
You become more clear of old
mental emotional patterns

00:54:41.420 --> 00:54:43.610 align:middle line:84%
of behavior you created
as a young child,

00:54:43.610 --> 00:54:46.340 align:middle line:84%
that helped you greatly at
that point in your life--

00:54:46.340 --> 00:54:49.360 align:middle line:84%
but as adults, oftentimes,
are not serving you.

00:54:49.360 --> 00:54:52.020 align:middle line:84%
You go home for the
holidays and you're

00:54:52.020 --> 00:54:54.020 align:middle line:84%
watching your mom and
dad, or sister or brothers

00:54:54.020 --> 00:54:55.230 align:middle line:90%
trigger you like crazy.

00:54:55.230 --> 00:54:57.000 align:middle line:84%
And you're actually a
four-year-old again.

00:54:57.000 --> 00:54:59.090 align:middle line:84%
Like, well, where do
these emotions come from?

00:54:59.090 --> 00:55:02.300 align:middle line:84%
They're stored memories of
stress in your fat cells

00:55:02.300 --> 00:55:05.210 align:middle line:84%
that remotely make you think
and do the same dumb stuff again

00:55:05.210 --> 00:55:06.030 align:middle line:90%
and again.

00:55:06.030 --> 00:55:09.990 align:middle line:84%
But as you become more still and
more self-aware, you then see,

00:55:09.990 --> 00:55:13.470 align:middle line:84%
oh, that's what's
happening here.

00:55:13.470 --> 00:55:15.680 align:middle line:84%
And then you see that not
just is there a door number

00:55:15.680 --> 00:55:18.440 align:middle line:84%
one, the old pattern of doing
the same dumb thing again

00:55:18.440 --> 00:55:19.500 align:middle line:90%
and again and again.

00:55:19.500 --> 00:55:21.740 align:middle line:84%
You begin to see
there's door number two.

00:55:21.740 --> 00:55:26.210 align:middle line:84%
I can-- instead of reacting
to their situation,

00:55:26.210 --> 00:55:30.190 align:middle line:84%
