joyful and kind.

00:55:33.370 --> 00:55:34.390 align:middle line:90%
And that's the trick.

00:55:34.390 --> 00:55:36.370 align:middle line:84%
That's the beauty
of self-awareness.

00:55:36.370 --> 00:55:39.490 align:middle line:84%
But what most people don't
get is the Vedic prescription

00:55:39.490 --> 00:55:43.420 align:middle line:84%
was establish being and
then perform action.

00:55:43.420 --> 00:55:46.090 align:middle line:84%
You can't Yoga, breathe,
meditate, and go lie, cheat,

00:55:46.090 --> 00:55:47.260 align:middle line:90%
and steal on your life.

00:55:47.260 --> 00:55:52.630 align:middle line:84%
You have to follow it up
with real, tangible actions.

