And I'm reacting to a version
of her that's not really her,

00:56:10.300 --> 00:56:12.490 align:middle line:84%
right, with the version of
me that's not really me.

00:56:12.490 --> 00:56:14.157 align:middle line:84%
Because I'm reacting
to a version of her

00:56:14.157 --> 00:56:15.370 align:middle line:90%
