01:05:30.780 --> 01:05:33.000 align:middle line:10%
a choice is made.

01:05:33.000 --> 01:05:36.000 align:middle line:10%
Now upon observation, one
of those possibilities

01:05:36.000 --> 01:05:39.520 align:middle line:10%
