01:06:26.850 --> 01:06:28.840 align:middle line:10%
And indeed, it could.

01:06:28.840 --> 01:06:31.530 align:middle line:10%
There have been many
indications and new discoveries

01:06:31.530 --> 01:06:34.750 align:middle line:10%
